- Status tracking: Paid/Pending/Overdue
- Fixed amount remains constant regardless of revenue

### Percentage-Based Revenue Share Model  
- Dynamic rent calculation based on stylist's weekly revenue
- Real-time preview calculations as revenue estimates change
- Automatic recalculation when revenue figures are updated

